high_descs: Turn left and walk to the toilet.
Pick up the candle from the back of the toilet.
Turn to face the cabinet below the sink.
Open the cabinet door, put the candle in the cabinet, and close the door.
Move to face the back of the toilet.
Pick up the candle to the left of the tube.
Move back over to face the cabinet below the sink.
Open the door, put the candle in the cabinet and close the door.
anns.task_desc: To move two candles to the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left and step forward to face the toilet.
Pick up the candle on the right of the back of the sink.
Take a step to the right to face the cabinet below the left side of the sink.
Place the candle in the cabinet on the left.
Take a step to the left to face the back of the toilet.
Pick up the candle on the right of the back of the sink.
Take a step to the right to face the cabinet below the left side of the sink.
Place the candle in the cabinet next to the first candle.
anns.task_desc: To place two candles in the left cabinet under the sink.

high_descs: Turn to the left and move towards the counter left of the sink.
Pick up the candle off the counter.
Turn around to back up from the counter and turn around again to face the cupboard underneath the counter.
Place the candle inside the cupboard.
Turn to the left and move toward the toilet on the right.
Pick up the candle on the middle of the toilet tank.
Turn around and move toward the cupboard beside the toilet.
Place the candle inside the cupboard.
anns.task_desc: Organize some of the candle sticks into the cupboard under the counter.
